[The serotype of EHEC is this outbreak is not stated. The prototypic serotype is, of course, O157:H7. The source of the outbreak organism may be produce such as tomato or lettuce that is served raw or undercooked meat. It is sometimes, unless the outbreak organism is isolated from the food, not easy to identify a specific source from food questionnaires. - Mod.LL

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4323887,216.]
